FBIS3-7864 "dreeu040_i_94023" FBIS-EEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Radio Brod Stops Broadcasting AU0103081794 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 0800 GMT 1 Mar 94 AU0103081794 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Text] Radio Brod, The Right To Speak [pravo na rec], which had broadcast programs for listeners on the territory of the former Yugoslavia, stopped broadcasting at midnight last night. The reason for this is the suspension of financial aid by the European Union.
